---
By: Peace Pilgrim
Locus:
  Page: 188
  Verse: 17
Tags:
  - ''
---
Do you know God? Do you know there is a power greater than ourselves which
manifests itself within us as well as everywhere else in the universe? This
I call God. Do you know what it is to know God, to have God’s constant
guidance, a constant awareness of God’s presence?
